T1  - A specification test for the propensity score using its distribution conditional on participation
AU  - Shaikh, Azeem M.
AU  - Simonsen, Marianne
AU  - Vytlacil, Edward J.
AU  - Yildiz, Nese
JO  - Journal of Econometrics
VL  - 151
